Class XADatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.derby.impl.drda.Database
      • org.apache.derby.impl.drda.XADatabase

  • class XADatabase
extends Database
    This class contains database state specific to XA, specifically the XAResource that will be used for XA commands.
